OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTony's Law: Plans for      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ftougher child abuse        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fsentences confirmed        
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Child abusers in England and Wales     
OL,6, could face life in jail under tougher  
OL,7, sentencing plans unveiled by ministers.
OL,9,FIt follows a campaign for Tony's Law by
OL,10,Fthe adoptive family of seven-year-old  
OL,11,FTony Hudgell, who had both legs        
OL,12,Famputated following abuse.             
OL,14,FJustice Secretary Dominic Raab said the
OL,15,Flegislation would provide "maximum     
OL,16,Fprotection to the most vulnerable".    
OL,18,FTony's adoptive mother Paula Hudgell,  
OL,19,Fof King's Hill, Kent, said she was     
OL,20,F"delighted" at the announcement.       
